{"tid":803600,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"六爻占卜","createTime":"2018-09-02T11:47:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T11:47:01.000Z","uid":178205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"595c5db98de8c867bd80ba15e8b4ae356c7f702a","tid":803600,"uid":178205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T11:47:01.000Z","msg":"一事一占，一支卦只可一件事<br />\n要問得仔細，同俾基本資料<br />\n例如<br />\n感情卦要俾性別，同埋default 係異性戀<br />\n事業你講下係待業還是做緊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n銅錢起卦方法<a href=\"https://www.eee-learning.com/learning/3coins.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eee-learning.com%2Flearning%2F3coins.htm&d=%2FgdtsKkrcp3hrtS81%2FU87EkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=a8beaa8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.eee-learning.com/learning/3coins.htm</a><br />\n心入面諗住想問既問題 然後擲3個銀仔 (最好係英女皇頭)<br />\n記錄每次既組合 total擲6次<br />\n<br />\n仲有記錄埋擲銀仔既日期時間 方便樓主起卦<br />\n<br />\n可以留tg詳談"}]}